{"tid":1351051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［光復元朗主線］727係突破「打人」呢個心理關卡的重要戰役","createTime":"2019-07-22T14:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:38:46.000Z","uid":274839,"like":129,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"09603ae7c507f409caab2708b297b7e9a3ce9c31","tid":1351051,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"先唔好屌我溝淡左上環單野。紅土同將軍澳都已經讓哂路，所以亦唔洗再討論係唔係真係要直入元朗。727元朗已經吹哂風，打硬架啦，唔好做架量。<br />\n<br />\n727元朗戰事，其實已經變左主線任務，原因有三：<br />\n1）警黑合作<br />\n2）無差別打人<br />\n3）觸動權貴<br />\n<br />\n之前好多人吹風話十八區最難搞就係元朗，明的，鄉黑權貴問題係真係好嚴重。但如果尋日上環你地有睇到，三十幾飛橡膠彈係咁射都無人反抗，無人打包圍戰個陣，你就明白有部份前線係對「戰爭」或者「打人」呢件事無咩概念。<br />\n<br />\n先由警黑合作講起。元朗出哂名係三不管地帶黎，尋日只不過將件事浮哂上水咁解。入面班差佬都要忌佢地三分，係元朗秩序理論「誰大誰惡誰正確」下，班差佬唔出手幫班黑已經算偷笑。最壞情況係班應變部隊入埋元朗，等你地劈緊友個陣就放催淚彈同噴椒，咁就一次過收哂網。<br />\n<br />\n無差別打人同觸動權貴就唔洗講。今次入元朗一戰係煉獄級任務黎，講緊而家係放哂風拆人祠堂同起人尾注，你認為佢地會有底線咁同你反抗？唔會囉，全港最大個三個黑幫收哂中共維穩費，聯手呀講緊，光明正大劈友呀，隨時會發展到好似以前日本侵華咁，鬥斬傷或者斬死幾多個人呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁但係點解仲要入元朗打？</strong><br />\n<br />\n要遍地開花，十八區光復點都要做，只不過因為尋日無差別打人先令大家明白呢件事唔可以再拖落去。<br />\n<br />\n今次挑戰煉獄級主線，樂觀d黎講就係幫自己升LV的最大機會。係呢次任務，你面對的係一班打開爛仔交的黑幫。佢地武器唔精良，但刀刀有力，佢地會話比你聽汽油彈真實係點樣用，佢地會圍毆。面家我地名正言順幫緊你班差佬做野，真正反黑。<br />\n<br />\n升LV固然重要，但今次元朗亦係拎光環的好機會。元朗黑問題一直以黎都解決唔到，係因為政權唔會親手落order清邨，利害關係太嚴重。今次元朗贏到的話，講緊係話比全香港知，我地勇武派就係最大的字頭，連政府搞唔掂的野我地藉住呢次推翻運動都幫你地搞掂埋。<br />\n<br />\n之後出番金鐘中環做下一條主線個陣，對家會驚到咩地步？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁點解可以衝破心理關口？</strong><br />\n<br />\n因為好大機會會死人。黑幫廝殺然後死人呢d新聞周不時都會見到，你唔劈到佢殘廢，佢就劈死你，唔死都至少要令你以後都生活唔撚到。<br />\n<br />\n其實同黑警打仗都係同一個概念，你唔衝散佢落單圍毆，佢地就會出椒出TG落棍毆到你仆街。但係前線對「見血」呢樣野仲係好似有潔癖咁，一見到血就要叫救護，打完先叫好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n我講到明先，元朗呢戰，要全贏先叫真係贏，唔係be water 就可以解決到的問題黎。起完人地祠堂之後班原居民一定會發癲，一定會打大交，一定見血。如果你真係咁不幸，比社團人點左相，出街諗下點樣保護自己啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住話叫差佬，你叫得佢地黎，佢唔出手打埋你一份，或者捉走你放班黑走都算偷笑。再者，鷹派二哥以前就係守元朗的，你話佢會唔會幫你地？最重點個樣野係，而家都無政府狀態緊，你仲靠個政權？<br />\n<br />\n要記住，邊個做架量，就準備比兩邊人一齊打。開拖最忌做架量，我點知你係咪內鬼？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁危險，咁要做d咩？</strong><br />\n<br />\n帶齊裝，因為當日絕大機會會出現「兩條」主線任務：黑，同警。所以事都要以至少4人一隊黎進行，人數多過自己個邊的就即走。<br />\n<br />\n今次元朗一定要學識包圍，同小隊攻勢。ok? 你學唔識，比人包住黎斬，講緊的唔係食TG落警棍咁簡單，而係真係可能無左條命，社團吹緊風，到時一個不留，女姦男殺呀。<br />\n<br />\n係元朗輸左d咩，我地727就要拎番返黎。順利的話，係鄉議會度成立埋臨立會都仲得。<span style=\"color: red;\">贏左，除左令黑永不翻身之外，仲講緊係直擊緊呢個政府權力來源的其中一角。輸左就香港正式宣布黑社會治港都得。</span><br />\n<br />\n咁你地明點解今次係主線未？"},{"pid":"ae8ffd6b7240dc5bd4c89310161566852aa7a7a2","tid":1351051,"uid":160506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"push, 唔好比達狗post洗板<br />\n<br />\n希望醒水嘅連登仔幫手推返上環post同有用post"},{"pid":"d654588316ef022735a468fe3705a51b14813191","tid":1351051,"uid":274839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"利申番<br />\n<br />\n呢堆野都係樓主發夢個陣夢到，驚得濟想警惕下大家。<br />\n<br />\n樓主唔不鼓吹大家犯罪。香港人係守法的良好公民黎。"},{"pid":"71c71fe0cecc06860649db393399c578b4ce330f","tid":1351051,"uid":285368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuAh7yF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuAh7yF.png&h=545c7de6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc32e8b5e5d2e10da557967fa51a06991d4d1fa","tid":1351051,"uid":123943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"【727光復元朗前哨戰】係元朗西鐵站外搞「元朗恐襲」放映會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00dafed0c27a044b7753233b7df386375b8428ee","tid":1351051,"uid":60000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"我地要和平 <br />\n人地打果時 唔還手 要講多謝人地"},{"pid":"e22f4590e5a9cd4d67710c6efc602641b462136f","tid":1351051,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"香港有冇棒球港隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e199cd62dd79831c6124227109e2d4c25fe7bb","tid":1351051,"uid":20431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"覺得應該開頭遊行和平，聚集多啲人先，之後大家自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果光復元朗失敗的話，我覺得啲人驚下驚下越來越少人出嚟"},{"pid":"58d0d1f47dd97fa5efbde1dcd0c384b88bb121c6","tid":1351051,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e199cd62dd79831c6124227109e2d4c25fe7bb","tid":1351051,"uid":20431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"覺得應該開頭遊行和平，聚集多啲人先，之後大家自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果光復元朗失敗的話，我覺得啲人驚下驚下越來越少人出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"而家冇人想再行散步日"},{"pid":"5118999b825b18e0ace80938053ff0e1ffae3c65","tid":1351051,"uid":2864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"對準政權<br />\n唔好主動走去打人<br />\n唔係就變左民眾鬥民眾"},{"pid":"1e6c356091f68eef8955fb20d69b6fbfba8c82a9","tid":1351051,"uid":20431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d0d1f47dd97fa5efbde1dcd0c384b88bb121c6","tid":1351051,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e199cd62dd79831c6124227109e2d4c25fe7bb","tid":1351051,"uid":20431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"覺得應該開頭遊行和平，聚集多啲人先，之後大家自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果光復元朗失敗的話，我覺得啲人驚下驚下越來越少人出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"而家冇人想再行散步日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"即係你預計到時即刻開片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3de7473e425ba4c88b1fc5bb6decd2288ab0e5f","tid":1351051,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n<br />\n[臨立會議程-臨立會秘書處] 六大訴求，民防與光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349179</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"207dbaa7bccaa1f38c0e2222b77fa1cfbe316093","tid":1351051,"uid":54389,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"傻啦，經過尋晚，香港一般市民已經默許打人"},{"pid":"ea9cf57f9087ffa872fba9551ec9159f46883012","tid":1351051,"uid":60000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"207dbaa7bccaa1f38c0e2222b77fa1cfbe316093","tid":1351051,"uid":54389,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"傻啦，經過尋晚，香港一般市民已經默許打人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"岩阿 被打完人 要求人地唔好打 跪低求人"},{"pid":"80ede370d4f75e2e7d5eae69dd91314218b74f87","tid":1351051,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"政府黑金請人打人就係想拉仇恨去小怪度<br />\n引你地去打佢 再拉晒我地義士<br />\n危險無獎勵副本勿去"},{"pid":"7da541a6e3a3d6883abd4f179872f63100ee0bde","tid":1351051,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd6ba718b81e304d1eea1b2d7b08048067694b88","tid":1351051,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c6a3eadfe7ff5fa828b7a9c768eaf5dda030e0","tid":1351051,"uid":268935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbdb13f21c8e11402f30cac640cd8e6e769fe74","tid":1351051,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00dafed0c27a044b7753233b7df386375b8428ee","tid":1351051,"uid":60000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"我地要和平 <br />\n人地打果時 唔還手 要講多謝人地"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"同朱議員手索索愉快咁築起人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能出手，不能互毆（from朱凱廸fb)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用愛與和平感化黑社會"},{"pid":"b98c5675edc2506e1c027f374a7352fa1045c759","tid":1351051,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:45:36.000Z","ms